snippet.title: Terra Nil | Coming March 28 | PC & Netflix
snippet.description:
Coming to PC & Netflix on March 28 | Pre-order at http://terranil.com

Pre-order on PC for a free upgrade to the Deluxe Edition which includes the Original Soundtrack and Digital Artbook.

Free Lives will donate a portion of their profits from Terra Nil on Steam to the Endangered Wildlife Trust. Visit https://ewt.org.za/ for more information.

Terra Nil is an intricate environmental strategy game about transforming a barren wasteland into a thriving, balanced ecosystem. Bring life back to a lifeless world by purifying soil, cleaning oceans, planting trees, and reintroducing wildlife, then leave without a trace.
